| Make `PiiRedactingExecutor._allSensitive` thread-safe via `Lazy<T>` | XS | `PiiRedactingExecutor.cs` |
| Add `SELECT`-only assertion in `ReadOnlyExecutor` using ScriptDom | S | `ReadOnlyExecutor.cs` |
| Add trace-save failure alerting (structured log with dedicated event ID + counter) | S | `CopilotTraceHistoryStore.cs` |

